data.description: Welcome to this custom home that boasts 4 BR's, and 4 1/2 baths. It sits on a sprawling 3 acre (+/-) lot, providing a blank canvas for anything you like! It also features high ceilings, warm hardwoods, a balcony, outdoor kitchen, and huge deck. Downstairs you will find 2 BR's/2.5 BA along with a large study, laundry room, wet bar, breakfast nook, formal dining room and a gourmet kitchen. Upstairs you will find 2 BR's/2 BA, a game room, media room, and a wet bar - perfectly setup for entertaining. The property also features a three car garage, water softener, and custom finishes throughout. The property is conveniently located near 249, making it easy to access nearby amenities and attractions. Tax rate is a very low 1.9%. Overall, this home is a fantastic opportunity for anyone looking for a private, comfortable, and stylish living space in the Tomball/Magnolia area. It also has an assumable 2.25% interest rate loan for those that qualify!
